title: Cloudstack projects
agents: linux
catalog: cloud/cloudstack
distribution: https://github.com/AlexanderStock/cloudstack_nagios
author: Alexander Stock <mail@stock-alexander.de>
license: GPL
description:
    This check is for monitoring the resource consumption of a cloudstack project
    in your cloud environment managed by cloudstack.

    Metrics you will receive from cloudstack are:
    'vm'
    'memory'
    'network'
    'snapshot'
    'volume'
    'ip'
    'vpc'
    'template'
    'primarystorage'
    'secondarystorage'

inventory:
  For each project a check in check_mk will be created.
